1. We have three matlab files
	a. question1.m
	b. question2.m
	c. Assignment3.m

2. Folder structure required
	a. The folder should have all the matlab files inside.
	b. The two folders containing the data should be also placed after extraction in the same folder.
	c. This main folder should be added to the path in Matlab.

	Main Folder
		-Human Activity Recognition (Folder)
		-VidTIMIT (Folder)
		-question1.m
		-question2.m
		-Assignment3.m

3. To run the code add the main folder to the path in Matlab and run the file Assignment3.m
